---
layout: base.njk
permalink: /Salon2/buvette/

title: "Buvette — Bien-Être et Créateurs 2026"
description: "Snacks et boissons sur place au salon Bien-Être et Créateurs. Tout à 1 €, ouvert samedi et dimanche de 10h à 18h."

hero:
  tag:       "Bien-Être et Créateurs · Sur place"
  titre:     "La"
  titreEm:   "Buvette"
  sousTitre: "Snacks & boissons · Tout à 1 €"

snacks:
  - nom: "Chips"
    prix: "1 €"
  - nom: "Mars"
    prix: "1 €"
  - nom: "Snickers"
    prix: "1 €"
  - nom: "Twix"
    prix: "1 €"
  - nom: "Financier aux amandes"
    prix: "1 €"
  - nom: "Rochers"
    prix: "1 €"
  - nom: "Pâte de fruit"
    prix: "0,50 €"

boissons:
  - nom: "Ice tea · Pepsi · Orangina (au verre)"
    prix: "1 €"
  - nom: "Capri Sun"
    prix: "1 €"
  - nom: "Thé · Infusion · Café"
    prix: "1 €"
  - nom: "Bouteille d'eau 50cl"
    prix: "1 €"

pageStyles: |
  .menus-grille {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .menu-bloc {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
    border: 1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.3);
    border-radius: 16px; padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    opacity: 0; animation: glisser-haut 0.7s ease forwards;
    transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
  }
  .menu-bloc:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(160,132,92,0.15); }
  .menu-bloc.snacks::before {
    content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--or), #e8c080);
  }
  .menu-bloc.boissons::before {
    content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--sauge), #90c090);
  }
  .menu-titre { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 300; color: var(--nuit); margin-bottom: 0.3rem; }
  .menu-emoji { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.8rem; display: block; }
  .menu-sous-titre { font-size: 0.6rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--terre); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; display: block; }
  .item-liste { list-style: none; }
  .item-liste li { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: 0.6rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.15); font-size: 0.8rem; }
  .item-liste li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .item-nom { color: var(--nuit); }
  .item-prix { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--terre); font-weight: 600; }
  .consigne { margin-top: 1rem; padding: 0.7rem 1rem; background: rgba(201,169,110,0.12); border: 1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.3); border-radius: 8px; font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--terre); text-align: center; }
  .info-buvette {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
    border: 1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.3);
    border-radius: 16px; padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px); text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    opacity: 0; animation: glisser-haut 0.7s ease forwards 1s;
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .info-buvette::before {
    content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--sauge), var(--or), var(--lotus));
  }
  .info-buvette p { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-style: italic; font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--terre); line-height: 1.7; }
  .footer-bloc { text-align: center; opacity: 0; animation: glisser-haut 0.8s ease forwards 1.1s; }
  @media(max-width: 500px) { .menus-grille { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
---

{# Hero #}
<div class="hero anime" style="animation-delay:0.2s">
  <span class="hero-tag">{{ hero.tag }}</span>
  <h1>{{ hero.titre }}<br><em>{{ hero.titreEm }}</em></h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">{{ hero.sousTitre }}</p>
</div>

<div class="sep">
  <div class="sep-l"></div><div class="sep-d"></div>
  <div class="sep-d" style="background:var(--sauge)"></div>
  <div class="sep-d"></div><div class="sep-r"></div>
</div>

<div class="menus-grille">

  {# Snacks #}
  <div class="menu-bloc snacks" style="animation-delay:0.5s">
    <span class="menu-emoji">🍫</span>
    <div class="menu-titre">Snacks</div>
    <span class="menu-sous-titre">Petites douceurs</span>
    <ul class="item-liste">
      {% for item in snacks %}
      <li><span class="item-nom">{{ item.nom }}</span><span class="item-prix">{{ item.prix }}</span></li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
  </div>

  {# Boissons #}
  <div class="menu-bloc boissons" style="animation-delay:0.65s">
    <span class="menu-emoji">☕</span>
    <div class="menu-titre">Boissons</div>
    <span class="menu-sous-titre">Fraîches &amp; chaudes</span>
    <ul class="item-liste">
      {% for item in boissons %}
      <li><span class="item-nom">{{ item.nom }}</span><span class="item-prix">{{ item.prix }}</span></li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
    <div class="consigne">🥤 Consigne verre : 1 €</div>
  </div>

</div>

<div class="info-buvette">
  <p>Une pause conviviale vous attend !<br>
  La buvette est ouverte toute la journée,<br>
  samedi et dimanche de 10h à 18h.</p>
</div>

<div class="footer-bloc">
  <a class="fb-lien" href="https://www.facebook.com/people/Bridge-Flow-Folk-BFF/61587252715739/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="16" height="16"><path d="M22 12c0-5.523-4.477-10-10-10S2 6.477 2 12c0 4.991 3.657 9.128 8.438 9.878v-6.987H7.898V12h2.54V9.797c0-2.506 1.492-3.89 3.777-3.89 1.094 0 2.238.195 2.238.195v2.46h-1.26c-1.243 0-1.63.771-1.63 1.562V12h2.773l-.443 2.89h-2.33v6.988C18.343 21.128 22 16.991 22 12z"/></svg>
    Suivre Bridge &amp; Flow Folk
  </a>
  <footer>© 2026 Bridge &amp; Flow Folk · Nogent-le-Roi (28) · 06 18 29 18 73</footer>
</div>
